rComments: She did a good job at trying to make 3 hour zoom lectures more bearable, and overall I really enjoyed her class. If you do all the readings and understand her lectures quizzes and exams are easy. It was easy to see how much she really cared about her student's success.

Prof really cared about her students. Mainly would read off slides, most content in the lecture came from the textbook. She made the 3 hour lecture go by so quick. Provided additional links about the content after the lecture. 3 quizzes, each worth 10%, 30% final paper, and 30% final. Reading the textbook is important for passing this class!!

I had my first class with her and already love her. She's so caring and really understands the struggle of online classes and nursing students in general. We need more profs like her who encourage us to do our best and inspire us to actually pursue a career in nursing. Amazing prof!
